comment: Always exceeds my expectations!

Love his work & so do customers Dolan Geiman’s pieces really elevate our space. Many of his works have a very cool SW vibe that fits our market perfectly. The quality of these prints and the framing system are absolutely elegant!
I love these prints! excellent quality. I ordered the large owl print to be a backdrop for an upcoming concert at our art center. It looks beautiful on the wall in it's star studded frame.
Great experience with orders Everything has been very smooth. Dolan is easy to reach and responds promptly. My materials arrived quickly and well packaged. Thanks!
Great Thank you - we love Dolans artwork and we appreciate the free shipping for one year and the $100. Off our first order. Thank you

Phenomenal  This company has the most beautiful, brilliant artwork, the most amazing, capable, helpful staff, and whoever packs the product for shipping looks like they went thru a PhD program for shipping art. Stellar in every aspect…..I’m a customer for life!

LOVE LOVE LOVE

The best! Not only do I love the art in our home, my customers love it! Shipping is fast, never damaged, and of course the art is amazing!

Multiple orders in and still amazed! Great product that sells itself. Children love them too - it's so fun to find all the "hidden treasures" in each piece. Love the colors; very vibrant. Dolan and his team are the best! Will definitely be back to purchase more.
Sells quickly! Always great and super fast shipping! Customer favorite. Goes with everyone's decor or style. Burro ones sell best for us. Pleasure doing business with Dolan and his team.
everything looks fabulous!  I can't wait to put in my store!

delightful and eager to see what sells first Things are very carefully packed. Exciting to see the new pieces!

The best! Amazing art that sells itself! Davina is very helpful and responsive. She’s also incredibly knowledgeable and can assist with what pieces you should start with. I’d love to have my whole store filled with Dolan’s art! It’s fun, bright and attracts customers of all ages. Thanks for another great experience!
Always fast, packaged very well and the pieces are so great!
Excellent

A+++++++ No words can express how amazing these products are! Customers love looking for the "hidden" messages and pictures. Customer service is the best too - Davina is so helpful and fast to reply to messages. We are on our 5th order in just a few months. Place your order now!!!
LOVE LOVE LOVE
Dolan Geiman prints We love Dolan's art! His art is the best, and love promoting him and his team! Brian

Color and texture oh my! :) We were only carrying the prints and framed prints when Davina suggested we might try a framed canvas. We choose Father Nature. We placed it behind our sales counter. Front and center. Talk about a conversation piece. The beauty of the larger canvas is you can really see the detail and find all of the hidden treasures in the piece. Father Nature has already found a home. It was a surprise birthday for a very lucky lady. We have ordered a second Father Nature and added a Cactus Country.
Love the new pieces!  The detail is amazing! Customers stare at them to see all the individual papers used to make your prints. Couldn’t be happier with the whole process!

Amazing - super talented! We are honored to be among their stockist. Just received our first order for my store - but my first purchase was for me personally over 15 years ago. Incredibly talented. Rearranged our store just for his pieces. Can't wait to get them on the sales floor. Thank you for your quick responses, valuable information and marketing materials too! Photo coming soon.

Beautiful Artwork! Since my shop is in a small tourist town west of Denver, I am always on the look out for new Colorado Artists for my retail shop. I found this amazing art and artist, and have had a great response selling them in my shop. I highly recommend this company!

Attention to detail... I love having Dolan's work in my store. His story, his process, his work are all top notch! The quality for the price point in on point.

My new favorite artist Dolan Geiman and is team are excellent to work with! My customers are loving the new prints and I love how quickly the product arrives. Definitely recommend this vendor.

UTTER FABULOUSNESS! Being a fine art gallery, handling only original works of contemporary art we were hesitant about carrying prints. After seeing them in person we came straight back to work and placed our first order. They are some of our top sellers and as soon as we get an order in we are having to restock - they sell THAT fast! Great company to work with!
